```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User types https://www.google.com in browser] --> B[DNS Resolution]
    B --> |DNS Query| C[DNS Server returns Google IP address]
    C --> D[Browser connects to server IP on port 443]
    
    D --> E[Traffic is encrypted with HTTPS/TLS]
    E --> F[Encrypted request goes through firewall]
    
    F --> G[Request distributed by load balancer]
    G --> H[Load balancer selects web server]
    
    H --> I[Web server receives request]
    I --> J[Web server forwards to application server]
    
    J --> K[Application server processes request]
    K --> L[Application server requests data from database]
    L --> M[Database returns data]
    M --> N[Application server generates web page]
    
    N --> O[Web server serves the web page]
    O --> P[Response goes back through load balancer]
    P --> Q[Response passes through firewall]
    Q --> R[Encrypted response sent to user]
    R --> S[User sees Google homepage in browser]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style B fill:#fff3e0
    style E fill:#ffecb3
    style F fill:#ffcdd2
    style G fill:#f3e5f5
    style K fill:#e8f5e8
    style L fill:#fff8e1
    style S fill:#c8e6c9
```
